data.description: Take a look at the SE Tulare beauty. Great for first time home buyers or adding it to your rental portfolio. This home has a nice open floor plan and is on a spacious lot. Near shopping, schools and highway 99 for your convenience. Perfect time to get you in before the holidays. Call or message for a private tour.
